  <article id="careers" class="main">
    	<header>
		<h1>Careers</h1>
	</header>
	<section class="quote">
	    <blockquote>		  
		    <p>&ldquo;I have always believed that great culture attracts the best people, <strong>and the best people attract the best clients.&rdquo;</strong></p>
		    <cite>&ndash; Neil Mortine</cite>		  		  
	    </blockquote>	
	</section>
	<section class="bound" style="overflow:visible;">	
		<div id="bg-instagram"></div>
		<div id="careers_culture" class="culture">
			<!-- Instagram -->
			<div id="instagram-link"><p>Follow us on <a class="blue-bg" target="_blank" href="https://instagram.com/fahlgrenmortine/">instagram</a> to see more!</p></div>
		</div>
		<div class="text">
			<p><strong>It's our philosophy, and we live it every day at Fahlgren Mortine.</strong> We hear it a lot (it's even painted on our walls), but that's because it's true. We do everything we can to foster a collegial, collaborative culture while promoting a healthy work-life balance so that we can recruit and retain the industry's best people, who want to do great things for great clients.</p>
	        <p id="careers_offerings" class="list">We offer:</p>
	        <ul>
	            <li>Competitive salaries</li>
	            <li>Health, dental and vision insurance</li>
	            <li>401(k) retirement savings plan with company match</li>
	            <li>Generous paid time off</li>
	            <li>Fahlgren Mortine University – an agency-wide professional development program</li>
	            <li>Philanthropy programs</li>
	            <li>Formal on-boarding process</li>
	            <li>Frequent <a href="http://www.facebook.com/fahlgrenmortine" rel="external" target="_blank" class="nopjax">culture-centric celebrations</a> – happy hours, miniature golf tournaments, kickball games, corn-on-the-cob-eating contests, and more</li>
	            <li>Paid internship/scholarship program</li>
	        </ul>			
	        <p>If you could see yourself at Fahlgren Mortine, submit your cover letter, resume and salary requirements, or <a href="https://careers-fahlgrenmortine.icims.com/jobs/intro" rel="external" target="_blank" class="nopjax">view our open positions</a>.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>        
	</section>
